share:

   The Way of the Warrior: An Ancient Path to Inner Peace is an
   exploration of what it means to experience and establish peace in your
   life. Cultural pioneer and thought leader Erwin Raphael McManus guides
   readers to a deeper understanding of their inner workings and provides
   the guidance you need to establish peace and tranquility in your home,
   neighborhood, communities, and even the world. Through understanding
   and cultivating peace, you can become the warrior you were created to
   be!

Scroll for more

BOOK CLUBS

The Way of the Warrior: An Ancient Path to Inner Peace is a movement of
people choosing to live a life of nobility, sacrifice, and fight the battles
of their inner world so they can win the battles of the outside world! Join
us in creating this movement with your family and friends and be part of a
book club today!

