ERWIN RAPHAEL McMANUS

Author of national bestseller
The Artisan Soul

   logo-white logo-white

lead pastor of
Mosaic in Los Angeles

   Erwin is an iconoclast, artist, and cultural thought leader known for
   his integration of creativity and spirituality. He is the founder and
   Lead Pastor of Mosaic, a Los Angeles based church of faith recognized
   as one of America’s most influential and innovative churches.

